QAMESTAM AAVGULLGHI UYVASAGHQELLGHILLU
Pelaasim Apellgha

Enkaam angyaghtuulluteng tawaten, angyaghnaq kayaalinghani enkaam taakut qamestii aqfaluki angaghqughluki unaangupiglluku siqineq quulvaghqaaqestanghani pegget sangwaat kayutkelluki angaghqumun.
Enkaam ighlekaqegkangit, whangkutaqun kayuteteng.

Taakut ama tawaten uyvasaghqelget.
Eghqwaaqaghluteng ama tawaten, taawa apeghiin'ghata eghqwaaneghmeng elngaatall piliighunneqeggsaatkayuk qamestam mangtaganeng.

Aavgughluki naten umutatkiita qamestam amestaallghi, mangteghanun awalightuutkaqiit.

Wetku tawani nengighqaqiit.
Mangteghaq qamaglluku.
Enkaam tawaten ama imiisalek sameng piyukegkameggneng.
Enkaangam aghnaghaghhaatlu awalightumun, awalightughyuneghtughqaagaqii.
Imiisaagut akileghtuusat amalka.
Aghnaaghaghaat sameng neqmeng neghyugnameng piiqluki, enkaam ayghighlutengllu awaalightughnaqaqelghiit.

Taawa taaqen'ghaata teghruughaaghes taakut petugaqelghiit aagram qulangakun.
